Package: PSIndependenceTest
Title: Independence Tests for Two-way, Three-way and Four-way Contingency Tables
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Piotr", "Sulewski", , "piotr.sulewski@apsl.edu.pl", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0788-6567"))
Description: Presentation two independence tests for two-way, three-way and four-way contingency tables. These tests are: the modular test and the logarithmic minimum test. For details on this method see: Sulewski (2018) <doi:10.1080/02664763.2018.1424122>, Sulewski (2019) <doi:https://doi.org/10.2478/bile-2019-0003>, Sulewski (2021) <doi:10.1080/00949655.2021.1908286>.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
